| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2254 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f3f87f38-e26f-5f59-8161-9d39df3dfbe1"
